ZH: 能否给我一些建议？
EN: Can you give me some advice?

ZH: 能否帮我打开这个文件？
EN: Could you help me open this file?

ZH: 能否告诉我你的电话号码？
EN: Can you tell me your phone number?

ZH: 能否再等一会儿？
EN: Can you wait a little longer?

ZH: 能否请你帮我买几个苹果？
EN: Could you please help me buy some apples?

ZH: 能否允许我晚一点到达？
EN: Can I arrive a little later?

ZH: 能否请你帮我查一下这个问题？
EN: Could you please help me look up this issue?

ZH: 能否借我一本书？
EN: Can you lend me a book?

ZH: 能否问一下你的年龄？
EN: May I ask your age?

ZH: 能否再说一遍，我没听清楚。
EN: Can you say it again? I didn't hear clearly.

ZH: 能否给我更多的时间？
EN: Can you give me more time?

ZH: 能否告诉我怎么走？
EN: Can you tell me how to get there?

ZH: 能否让我看一下你的笔记？
EN: May I have a look at your notes?

ZH: 能否请你帮我寄这封信？
EN: Could you please help me send this letter?

ZH: 能否请你替我拿一下这个东西？
EN: Can you please get this thing for me?

ZH: 能否请你再解释一下这个问题？
EN: Can you please explain this issue again?

ZH: 能否让我使用一下你的电脑？
EN: Could you let me use your computer for a moment?

ZH: 能否为我安排一间安静的房间？
EN: Can you arrange a quiet room for me?

ZH: 能否告诉我你的电子邮件地址？
EN: Can you tell me your email address?

ZH: 能否请你帮我确认一下时间？
EN: Could you please help me confirm the time?

ZH: 能否再试一次？
EN: Can we try again?
